data.description: Don't pass up on this amazing opportunity! This charming brick home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms has undergone a complete renovation and is now ready for its new owners. Situated on a spacious 1.89-acre lot, the property features a convenient U-shaped driveway with a newly poured parking pad. The home boasts numerous desirable features, including updated bathrooms with beautiful tiled walk-in showers. Additionally, the windows, septic tank, HVAC system, and flooring have all been replaced. Furthermore, the parking pad has been wired for an RV hookup, complete with water access. Don't miss out on all that this property has to offer!
